:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
\partial_{t}\eta+u_{01}\partial_{x}\eta=\frac{-i}{\rho_{1}}\frac{kA_{1}\left(e^{k\eta}-e^{-k\eta+2kh_{1}}\right)}{\omega-ku_{01}}e^{ikx-i\omega t};\\
